  moved to stable.

*openrc-0.6.1-r3 (18 Aug 2010)

  18 Aug 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +openrc-0.6.1-r3.ebuild:
  new ebuild intended for unmasking. Auto-VLAN support should now work.
  netif.lo moved to sysinit runlevel.

*openrc-0.6.1-r2 (14 Aug 2010)

  14 Aug 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> openrc-0.6.1-r2.ebuild:
  New revision of Funtoo core networking stuff - quite a few changes in
  this release.

*openrc-0.6.1-r1 (10 Aug 2010)

  10 Aug 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> openrc-0.6.1-r1.ebuild:
  New release with new core network stuff - many improvements have been made.
  Masked for testing.

